        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Using immunocytochemistry and super-resolution STED microscopy, DARP-32 was found to be localized as clusters in dendritic spines of cultured striatal neurons.. Experimental description: \"The postsynaptic localization of DARPP-32 in dendritic spines was studied in cultured striatal neurons (derived from E18.5 Sprague dawley rat embryos)\"" ;
